  "remarks": "Nikolai Gusev is the General Director of JSC “State Design Bureau ‘Vympel’ named after I.I. Toropov”, which is a leading Russian missiles manufacturer. JSC “State Design Bureau ‘Vympel’ named after I.I. Toropov” produces air-to-air and air-to-surface guided missiles, guided missiles for land and sea anti-aircraft systems, launchers, and catapults for airborne guided missiles, beam holders for suspension of aerial bomber armament and units for unguided aircraft missiles.",
